title: Which QB you'd want for the next 5 years & Game Of Thrones recap
itunes:title: Which QB you'd want for the next 5 years & Game Of Thrones recap
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined by both Handsome Hank and Matt "Money" Smith inside Studio 66! The guys first made fun of Russell Wilson's awkward video announcing he has re-signed and then quickly got into the net worth of Wilson's wife Ciara (1:00). Next up, the trio discussed Tiger Woods' Masters win and what they deem the greatest sports moments of all-time (10:20)? Then, the guys got into which other quarterbacks would you want for the next five seasons besides Russell Wilson (36:30)? Finally, Shek, Hank, Money & Eddie Spaghetti wrapped up the show with some Game Of Thrones episode one review and what they expect for next Sunday (52:10).
